{"tid":1460740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[佛教黃允畋] 趙崇威呢條冷血教畜 似乎好撚想出名","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:57:36.000Z","uid":52658,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4a50d0eb4c61a77d39ccc657d2f6b8cf9f8e5d0d","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbfk0d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvbfk0d2.png&h=4e2ff524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUzJX1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUzJX1g.png&h=9be97e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條友係佛教黃允畋中學教書<br />\n花名：趙傻閪<br />\n好撚中意輕薄d女仔<br />\n比人投訴過幾次<br />\n之前教DT 後尾DT成科摺左走去教數學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢個底花晒 一人一信幫佢埋單</span></strong></span><br />\n佢情緒咁唔穩定 不糾散播仇恨言論<br />\n我睇佢都係唔適合再教書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教到d學生變殺人犯咁點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條光頭肥佬 我都忍撚得你耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d77d8f9391970d5b999da7da1d74e0e05401408","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2942b2396a9bf6bbb442ba1f9d94dfdf0fb945a0","tid":1460740,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"批鬥佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8440f943fffcfa8d6fe5eaedf97de6b110fb801","tid":1460740,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"54e823ac95510d9f76318981aa8b2be55689f5ef","tid":1460740,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec9d280060a0770b03a92958674cdaea8da62c56","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2942b2396a9bf6bbb442ba1f9d94dfdf0fb945a0","tid":1460740,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"批鬥佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"有無人寫投訴信<br />\n無就我寫<br />\n好撚想呢條肥佬仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb36bb9ac854de3f93e4f55e775e76b6f4f083a4","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc2f30904e93644dbbdd64ae90bdc30452df2fa","tid":1460740,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"正宗教畜"},{"pid":"3ef0a7d91f02e60a24de9e6c63d430f17717ace9","tid":1460740,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"有冇email?<br />\n有我即寫"},{"pid":"2fb265baf7b9c2f516d4262178026bda0a560353","tid":1460740,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"推爆佢，呢件人形脂肪簡直係黃允畋最大嘅負資產，攞嚟堆填都嫌臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebdf08258d68a307cc3280ec2aaa4a59064ec42","tid":1460740,"uid":5