d":"7a589756fb5318e337539b1505ff85c704773873","tid":1460740,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位爸爸媽媽見到咁既人教你仔女都咪話唔驚"},{"pid":"74f4ad8d14c0899494e0e6b4eb1ee84882786f45","tid":1460740,"uid":224375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n真名：趙崇威<br />\n花名：趙傻閪</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06e93c1af2174b02a5bb0e6b5c30fb390d9de6","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d557113c68317ec70f29bd496ee20e7d8c60832","tid":1460740,"uid":277501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e823ac95510d9f76318981aa8b2be55689f5ef","tid":1460740,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJWMbrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJWMbrz.jpg&h=6d3200ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無恥！敢做唔敢認，有冇方法幫佢搵「真兇」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"鼓吹殺人 散播仇恨<br />\n夠唔夠釘佢牌？"},{"pid":"e78055b5a3ee5db77d3b8c3bbf55a45bad1f193f","tid":1460740,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"又係DT，之前好似有post討論過DT阿sir大部分都咸濕佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe313fc2a5d48d3e21f3dfaf96f74b391aee05","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"仲要投訴埋間學校<br />\n出左d咁既老師 我仲點敢比我小朋友係度讀書<br />\n個校長好要面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今鋪佢聽仆街"},{"pid":"720d9fe47c980bb58469f11eef5158f3da9d724b","tid":1460740,"uid":83650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"Email: info@bwwtc.edu.hk<br />\nTopic: 有關貴校趙崇威老師於網上散播仇恨及殘忍言論<br />\nContent: <br />\n敬啓者,<br />\n<br />\n近日基於社會動盪, 市民大眾一般於網上社交媒體發表有關個人就事件之意見, 此舉無可厚非亦表現出香港社會言論自由之可貴。<br />\n<br />\n然 貴校趙崇威老師就有關事件於其社交媒體所發表之言論實在令人齒冷。作為教育學生之身份, 因著個人政治立場而說出「爆眼不足夠...烏合之眾死有餘辜。是學生亦不值可憐」此等語句(詳見附件具名, 時間之截圖), 令人懷疑趙崇威老師作為教育者身份對學生關愛之心態是否有所扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n此次致函乃希望貴校就趙崇威老師之言論作出回覆如何處理, 相信作為佛教辦學團體學校, 絕對希望對學生以致社會上之弱勢階層表現關愛同理之感情。再次重申, 趙崇威老師之言論與校訓「明智顯悲」相違, 更令人擔憂其能否足以擔當教育者之身份。如貴校未能作出回覆, 有關資料將交予各大媒體作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n祝 工安,<br />\n市民xxx<br />\n13.08.2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.s記得加埋圖"},{"pid":"706a08a629f9a9040d11f731edb26b018e603646","tid":1460740,"uid":85030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"sent<br />\n<br />\nDear Principal Yip<br />\n<br />\nI'm writing to lodge a complaint against one of your teachers 趙崇威 who spread hate speech on social media (see attached).<br />\n<br />\nA teacher is a figure which many students look up to. Spreading hate speech on social media is neither a responsible nor ethical act. I believe an investigation into whether Chiu is professionally fit to carry out his teaching duties should be in place. The last thing we would want to see is our students being manipulated into spreading hate against each other.<br />\n<br />\nI'm also keeping the Hong Kong Professional Teachers' Union informed of my grave concerns. Your written reply is highly appreciated. <br />\n<br />\nThank you very much<br />\nA Hong Kong citizen"},{"pid":"c796030ce6466592bfc1a2d0410d53ab4422d6cb","tid":1460740,"uid":277501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"學生、家長、校友、教職員都多得佢唔少，校譽一朝喪！佢而家唔認，係咪就無佢符？"},{"pid":"e5fe6bd21abad4c225d27026ead896f2f28a64db","tid":1460740,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720d9fe47c980bb58469f11eef5158f3da9d724b","tid":1460740,"uid":83650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"Email: info@bwwtc.edu.hk<br />\nTopic: 有關貴校趙崇威老師於網上散播仇恨及殘忍言論<br />\nContent: <br />\n敬啓者,<br />\n<br />\n近日基於社會動盪, 市民大眾一般於網上社交媒體發表有關個人就事件之意見, 此舉無可厚非亦表現出香港社會言論自由之可貴。<br />\n<br />\n然 貴校趙崇威老師就有關事件於其社交媒體所發表之言論實在令人齒冷。作為教育學生之身份, 因著個人政治立場而說出「爆眼不足夠...烏合之眾死有餘辜。是學生亦不值可憐」此等語句(詳見附件具名, 時間之截圖), 令人懷疑趙崇威老師作為教育者身份對學生關愛之心態是否有所扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n此次致函乃希望貴校就趙崇威老師之言論作出回覆如何處理, 相信作為佛教辦學團體學校, 絕對希望對學生以致社會上之弱勢階層表現關愛同理之感情。再次重申, 趙崇威老師之言論與校訓「明智顯悲」相違, 更令人擔憂其能否足以擔當教育者之身份。如貴校未能作出回覆, 有關資料將交予各大媒體作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n祝 工安,<br />\n市民xxx<br />\n13.08.2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.s記得加埋圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於有次唔係自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df793d9e8ffdf6923c9db2fd2d5a9917726e398","tid":1460740,"uid":265752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔好再容忍佢，條友可以有咁多舊生對佢不滿，絕對唔會係巧合！"}]}